org.apache.archiva.repository.features

Class ArtifactCleanupFeature

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.archiva.repository.features.ArtifactCleanupFeature
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RepositoryFeature<ArtifactCleanupFeature>

    public class ArtifactCleanupFeature
extends Object
implements RepositoryFeature<ArtifactCleanupFeature>
    This feature provides settings for artifact cleanup. This is meant mainly for snapshot artifacts, that should be deleted after a time period.
